                        <h2>Managed Disks<span>Managed Disks</span></h2>
                        <h4>Use Azure Virtual Machine permanent and secure managed disk storage</h4>
                        <em><a href="/pricing/1rmb-trial/" id="home_site_trial_storage-Managed-Disks">Apply for 1RMB Trial<i class="icon icon-arrow-right-thin"></i></a></em> <a href="/pricing/pia/" id="home_site_pia_storage-blobs">Buy Now<i class="icon icon-arrow-right-thin"></i></a>
